  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. (You confirmed this can be shared.) Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">A network visualization and management app where users build graphs of nodes and links, then analyze the resulting structure with force-directed layout and graph metrics. The v2 rebuild adds AI-powered node generation and multiple import formats (Obsidian, Mermaid, CSV).</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A dense ownership network built and explored in Connectology\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/connectology/network.png\" alt=\"A dense ownership network built and explored in Connectology\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/connectology/network.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/connectology/network.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/connectology/network.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/connectology/network.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A dense ownership network built and explored in Connectology\" width=\"1736\" height=\"1556\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1736×1556\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A dense ownership network built and explored in Connectology</figcaption>\n</figure>",
